HOUSE BILL NO. HB0070
Irrigation districts-bid requirements.
Sponsored by: Joint Corporations, Elections & Political
Subdivisions Interim Committee
A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to irrigation districts; increasing the
2 cost requirements for irrigation district purchases or
3 projects that are required to be submitted for bids; and
4 providing for an effective date.
5
6 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
7
8 Section 1. W.S. 41-7-412 and 41-7-813 are amended to
9 read:
10
11 41-7-412. Advertisement for bids.
12
13 In all cases where the work to be done at any one (1) time
14 under the direction of the commissioners will, in their
15 opinion, cost to exceed seven thousand five hundred dollars
1 HB0070

